\cs15\fs16\insrsid11292660 \chatn }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang1024\langfe1024\noproof\insrsid12657615 wonder}}}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3700453 . {\*\atrfstart 415577385}
Men accompanied him, and at length they saw on the surf-beaten shore a woman with long tawny hair, dressed in a queer garb of colored bird skins, and scraping with a bone knife the blubber from a seal. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs16 \ltrch\fcs0 
\cs15\fs16\insrsid11292660 {\*\atrfend 415577384}{\*\atnid SS}{\*\atnauthor Sara Schwebel}\chatn {\*\annotation{\*\atnref 415577384}{\*\atndate 1731339652}\ltrpar \pard\plain \ltrpar
