ed no objection when by signs she was made to understand that she was to go with them in the boat.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs16 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs15\fs16\insrsid12657615 {\*\atrfend 415577385}{\*\atnid SS}{\*\atnauthor Sara Schwebel}\chatn 
